        "Title": "The Broken Oath of the Syndicate",
        "Location": "LOCATION_BANGKOK",
        "PublicId": "108386495270",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Bangkok/_scene_tiger.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository efb0894c-426e-4f66-9822-880d1e735047).Image",
        "Description": "Good Afternoon, 47.\r\rThe situation in Bangkok has escalated. Five Syndicate operatives are present at the Himmapan Hotel: Benjamin Bertram, Michael Emerson, Mrs. Mookjai, Holly, and Rama Yodsuwan. Yodsuwan is an undercover ICA agent who has defected and now aids the Syndicate. His access privileges pose a critical security risk. Eliminate all five to neutralize the Bangkok cell and contain the breach.\r\rDiscretion is paramount.\r\rGood luck, 47.",
